titleNullable: Quake 3 Arena Aqua Bones Model 28x28 RGB
descriptionNullable:
* [QUAKE3.zip](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mrbiid/quake-3-arena-aqua-bones-model-28x28/download?datasetVersionNumber=1) - 7,444 Samples RGB

I collected this dataset of 7,444 samples myself, initially manually and then assisted collection with automation but all images have been manually categorised.

They are split into two folders:
- Targets (aqua blue bones model images)
- NonTargets (random quake3 map background scenery)

[https://github.com/TFNN/DOCS/tree/main/DATASETS](https://github.com/TFNN/DOCS/tree/main/DATASETS)

**Implementation in Keras:** https://github.com/mrbid/QUAKE3_TENSOR_TRIGGER
